INGROUP: {{REPO_NAME}}
REPO: {{REPO_URL}}
PATH: /docs/file.md
VERSION: XX.YY.ZZ
BRIEF: One-line description
-->
```

**YAML / Shell:** Use `#` comments with the same fields. JSON files are exempt.

