## Version Management

**`README.md` is the single source of truth for the repository version.**

- The `VERSION: XX.YY.ZZ` field in the README.md `FILE INFORMATION` block governs all other version references.
- Update the version in `README.md` only ‚Äî the `sync-version-on-merge` workflow propagates it automatically to all badges and `FILE INFORMATION` headers on merge to `main`.
- Version format is zero-padded semver: `XX.YY.ZZ` (e.g. `04.00.04`).
- Never hardcode a specific version in document body text ‚Äî use the badge or FILE INFORMATION header only.

